{
    "publish_date": "2009-09-17T00:19:56.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT2M12S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Hope has the power to fill\nour lives with happiness.", 
            "dur": "7.05", 
            "start": "13.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hope sustains us through\ndespair.", 
            "dur": "4.42", 
            "start": "20.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We learn to cultivate hope the\nsame way we learn to walk, one", 
            "dur": "6.31", 
            "start": "25.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "step at a time.", 
            "dur": "3.5", 
            "start": "31.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We grow in our ability to\n&quot;abound in hope, through the", 
            "dur": "3.89", 
            "start": "35.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "power of the Holy Ghost,&quot;\nas we more", 
            "dur": "3.29", 
            "start": "38.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "perfectly live the gospel.", 
            "dur": "4.84", 
            "start": "42.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We hope in Jesus Christ, in the\ngoodness of God, in the", 
            "dur": "5.43", 
            "start": "47.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "manifestations of the Holy\nSpirit, in the knowledge that", 
            "dur": "4.32", 
            "start": "52.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "prayers are heard\nand answered.", 
            "dur": "4.46", 
            "start": "56.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hope teaches that there is\nreason to rejoice even when", 
            "dur": "3.54", 
            "start": "61.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all seems dark around us, no\nmatter how bleak the chapter", 
            "dur": "5.76", 
            "start": "64.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of our lives may look today.", 
            "dur": "3.07", 
            "start": "70.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because of the life and\nsacrifice of Jesus Christ, we", 
            "dur": "4.65", 
            "start": "73.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "may hope and be assured that the\nending of the book of our", 
            "dur": "5.15", 
            "start": "78.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "lives will exceed our grandest\nexpectations.", 
            "dur": "3.993", 
            "start": "83.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And to all who suffer--to all\nwho feel discouraged, worried,", 
            "dur": "5.44", 
            "start": "90.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or lonely--I say with love\nand deep concern for", 
            "dur": "3.85", 
            "start": "95.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you, never give in.", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "99.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Never surrender.", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "101.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Never allow despair to overcome\nyour spirit, for the", 
            "dur": "4.41", 
            "start": "103.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "love of the Son of God pierces\nall darkness, softens all", 
            "dur": "4.37", 
            "start": "108"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sorrow, and gladdens\nevery heart.", 
            "dur": "3.38", 
            "start": "112.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Of this I testify and leave you\nmy blessing in the name of", 
            "dur": "5.89", 
            "start": "115.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Jesus Christ, amen.", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "121.64"
        }
    ], 
